{"tid":1822461,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴絲做運動會頭暈眼花","createTime":"2020-01-13T03:49:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T05:28:56.000Z","uid":99219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6e522e82fa83927f66c7fc04cb936a5c2e1daaa5","tid":1822461,"uid":99219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T03:49:03.000Z","msg":"跑步唔夠10分鐘就開始頭暈 呼吸困難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後就放慢腳步 最後慢行 去到最後仲會眼花 連企都企唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇過幾次醫生 次次都話我少做運動 做返多d無事<br />\n但我keep左跑步半年（一星期最少一次）都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依個問題困擾左我幾年 有無巴絲都係咁 有無咩解決方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42a3de1cae8834ef0701bfcf23eefd233e4bc587","tid":1822461,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T03:50:49.000Z","msg":"血糖低？<br />\n輕微地中海窮血？"},{"pid":"c36518a1bc05abe60186c300b0ef98b155eecace","tid":1822461,"uid":114062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T03:50:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e84a873ced7ee72dcf4a3d9aaa70e2aea7c6acd","tid":1822461,"uid":99219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42a3de1cae8834ef0701bfcf23eefd233e4bc587","tid":1822461,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T03:50:49.000Z","msg":"血糖低？<br />\n輕微地中海窮血？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T03:54:05.000Z","msg":"應該唔係 細個果陣無問題 係高中開始會咁<br />\n同埋check過血壓同血含氧都無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我有食幾粒糖先出去跑步 應該唔會血糖低掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"675573f1855eed70a554dd684d170b0a3a387a1f","tid":1822461,"uid":99219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c36518a1bc05abe60186c300b0ef98b155eecace","tid":1822461,"uid"